    dc:description "FIGURE 5 Hungarocypris suranareeae n. sp., female (A, C – D, MSU-ZOC. 135), male (B, E, MSU-ZOC. 139). A. carapace, left lateral view; B. carapace, right lateral view; C. valve surface of A.; D. posterior part of A.; E. posterior part of B. Scale bar = 500 Μm for A – B; = 50 Μm for C; 100 Μm for D – E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/270575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270576>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6 Hungarocypris suranareeae n. sp., female (A – G, MSU-ZOC. 133), male (H – I, MSU-ZOC. 132). A. LV, internal view; B. RV, internal view; C. muscle scars of A.; D. postero-ventral part of A.; E. antero-ventral part of A.; F. antero-ventral part of B.; G. postero-ventral part of B.; H. LV, internal view; I. RV, internal view. Scale bar = 500 Μm for A – B, H – I; = 100 Μm for C – G." ;
