    dc:description "FIGURE 7 Hungarocypris suranareeae n. sp., female (MSU-ZOC. 133). A. A 1; B. A 2; C. enlargement of apical seta of second segment of A 2; D. Md-palp; E. terminal segment of Md-palp; F. Md-coxa. Scale bar = 100 Μm for A – B, D – F; 63 Μm for C." ;
